        "title": "How To Apply It",
        "body": "1. Show a live preview and the current style source.\n2. Keep presets inside the appearance section instead of giving them separate authority.\n3. Expose a small set of outcome-focused controls.\n4. Make reset-per-field or reset-all-overrides explicit.\n5. Hide or remove raw style editing from the normal surface.",
